text: Riedwihr () is a former commune in the Haut-Rhin department in Grand Est in north-eastern France. On 1 January 2016, it was merged into the new commune Porte-du-Ried.Arrêté 17 December 2015 ==References== Category:Former communes in Haut-Rhin Category:2016 disestablishments in France
title: Riedwihr
